### =========================================
### ELECTROCORP API TESTS
### Base URL
### =========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@ownerId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111


### =========================================
### HEALTH CHECK SIMPLE
### =========================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json


### =========================================
### DEVICES
### =========================================

### 1) Obtener todos los dispositivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json


### 2) Crear dispositivo 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}",
  "name": "Refrigeradora",
  "code": "DEV-001",
  "type": "SMART_PLUG"
}


### 3) Crear dispositivo 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}",
  "name": "Aire acondicionado",
  "code": "DEV-002",
  "type": "SMART_SWITCH"
}


### 4) Crear dispositivo 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}",
  "name": "Router principal",
  "code": "DEV-003",
  "type": "SENSOR"
}


### 5) Volver a listar dispositivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json


### =========================================
### IMPORTANTE:
### Copia aquí el id real de un device creado
### después de ejecutar el POST de arriba
### =========================================

@deviceId = REEMPLAZA_AQUI_EL_UUID_REAL


### 6) Encender dispositivo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{deviceId}}/turn-on
Accept: application/json


### 7) Apagar dispositivo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{deviceId}}/turn-off
Accept: application/json


### 8) Renombrar dispositivo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{deviceId}}/rename
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Refrigeradora Cocina"
}


### 9) Programar horario para dispositivo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{deviceId}}/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "executeAt": "18:30",
  "turnOn": true
}


### 10) Eliminar dispositivo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/{{deviceId}}
Accept: application/json


### =========================================
### ENERGY READINGS
### =========================================

### 11) Obtener todas las lecturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/readings
Accept: application/json


### 12) Registrar lectura energética
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/readings
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}",
  "amount": 10.5
}


### 13) Registrar otra lectura energética
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/readings
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "{{deviceId}}",
  "amount": 7.25
}


### 14) Volver a listar lecturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/readings
Accept: application/json


### =========================================
### ENERGY RECOMMENDATIONS
### =========================================

### 15) Obtener recomendaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/recommendations
Accept: application/json